                \n that each point charge would create in the absence of the others. That is,
                \n The electric field is nothing but the potential gradient of that particular point.
"
                        android:id="@+id/textAnswer9ElectromagneticFields"></TextView></LinearLayout></androidx.core.widget.NestedScrollView>
